contentList.content: After <LSTag Type="Spell" Tooltip="Shout_Dash">Dashing</LSTag> or taking a similar action, you can <LSTag Type="Spell" Tooltip="Projectile_Jump">Jump</LSTag> once that turn without using a bonus action.
Perform an offhand attack with your shield.
Your body is a chiseled monument to discipline, every scar a testament to your unbreakable will. You are ready to embrace glory or death without a whisper of fear.
